2. Drag video file or click ![](https://d3a7ykdi65m4cy.cloudfront.net/ac-en/s3fs-public/documentation/sdk/en/BPMonlineWebSDK/Screenshots/CustomizeFieldsFreedomUi/8.2/btn_UploadFileButton.png) to upload the video from your device.  
4. **Click Insert video**.
